"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/682964","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-02-06","<p>I refer the hon. Member to the answer I gave on 31 January to the hon. Member for Rutherglen and Hamilton West (Ms Ferrier) to Question 61464. HMS Vengeance successfully concluded her Demonstration and Shakedown Operation and returned to the operational cycle.</p>","Sevenoaks","Sir Michael Fallon","62562 ; 62565","2017-02-06T16:32:47.917Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/682964/answer","Biography information for Sir Michael Fallon","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/682964/answer","20170131_61464_WQnA_extract_on_Trident_Missile_Testing.docx","61464 - WQnA extract on Trident Missile Testing","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/682964/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-02-01","Trident Missiles: Testing","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what his Department's policy is on publication of the results of the Royal Navy SSBN and Trident II D5 demonstration and shakedown operations.","false","Biography information for Mr Kevan Jones","North Durham","Mr Kevan Jones","62655"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/682965","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-02-06","<p>There are no dates for Initial and Full Operating Capability for 12th and 20th Armoured Infantry Brigades, which already operate in the armoured infantry role. The brigades will receive incremental capability enhancements as their units receive the upgraded Warrior and Challenger 2, and new AJAX vehicles (formerly called Scout SV). The Ministry of Defence is expecting all of these vehicles to be in service by 2025.</p>","Hemel Hempstead","Mike Penning",,"2017-02-06T16:22:48.433Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/682965/answer","Biography information for Sir Mike Penning","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/682965/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/682965/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-02-01","Army","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, pursuant to the Answer of 17 January 2017 to Question 59886, when he plans for the (a) 12th and (b) 20th Armoured Infantry Brigade to reach initial operational capacity with upgraded Warrior, upgraded Challenger 2 and Scout vehicles; and when he plans for the (i) 12th and (ii) 20th Armoured Infantry Brigade to reach full operational capacity with that new equipment.","false","Biography information for Mr Kevan Jones","North Durham","Mr Kevan Jones","62656"
